<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        :root {
            --brand-red: #d32f2f;
            --brand-blue: #1a237e;
            --border-bold: 1.5px solid #000;
            --border-thin: 1px solid #000;
        }

        body {
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-size: 9.5px;
            /* High density like the reference image */
            color: #000;
        }

        .page-container {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            border: var(--border-bold);
        }

        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            table-layout: fixed;
        }

        td,
        th {
            border: var(--border-thin);
            padding: 3px 5px;
            vertical-align: top;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        /* Header Style */
        .main-header {
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 11px;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: var(--border-bold);
            padding: 2px;
        }

        .logo-area {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
        }

        .logo-img {
            max-height: 50px;
        }

        .company-title {
            color: var(--brand-red);
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 900;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .address-text {
            font-size: 8px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }

        /* Barcode Area */
        .barcode-box {
            text-align: center;
        }

        #barcode {
            width: 140px;
            height: 35px;
        }

        /* Vertical Labels */
        .vertical-text {
            writing-mode: vertical-rl;
            transform: rotate(180deg);
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            background: #e0e0e0;
            width: 20px;
        }

        /* Bold Labels */
        .label {
            font-weight: bold;
            display: block;
            font-size: 8px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 1px;
        }

        .value {
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 10px;
        }

        /* Charges Section */
        .bg-grey {
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
        }

        .total-row {
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
            background: #e0e0e0;
        }

        /* Conditions Section */
        .conditions-box {
            font-size: 6.5px;
            line-height: 1.1;
            padding: 5px;
            border-top: var(--border-bold);
        }

        .conditions-title {
            color: var(--brand-red);
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 9px;
            margin-bottom: 3px;
        }

        hr {
            border: 0;
            border-top: 1px solid #000;
            margin: 2px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="page-container">
        <div class="main-header">COURIER CONSIGNMENT NOTE ISSUED BY COMPANY</div>

        <table>
            <tr>
                <td colspan="4" class="logo-area" style="width: 50%;">
                    <% if(logo) { %>
                        <img src="<%= logo %>" class="logo-img">
                        <% } else { %>
                            <h1 class="company-title">Anushka Air Courier</h1>
                            <% } %>
                                <div class="address-text">
                                    PLOT NO 63, RADHA VIHAR, JAIPUR, RAJASTHAN - 302033
                                </div>
                </td>
                <td colspan="2">
                    <span class="label">Date:</span>
                    <span class="value">
                        <%= date %>
                    </span>
                    <hr>
                    <span class="label">TAX INVOICE - NO:</span>
                    <span class="value">
                        <%= document_number %>
                    </span>
                </td>
                <td colspan="2" class="barcode-box">
                    <span class="label">C.N.No.</span>
                    <svg id="barcode"></svg>
                    <div class="value">
                        <%= document_number %>
                    </div>
                </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
                <td colspan="2"><span class="label">PRODUCT:</span> <span class="value">
                        <%= type %>
                    </span></td>
                <td colspan="2"><span class="label">SERVICE:</span> <span class="value">
                        <%= service %>
                    </span></td>
                <td colspan="2"><span class="label">MODE:</span> <span class="value">
                        <%= travel_by %>
                    </span></td>
                <td colspan="2"><span class="label">VALUE OF GOODS:</span> <span class="value">₹<%= value %></span></td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
                <td class="vertical-text">CONSIGNOR</td>
                <td colspan="3">
                    <div class="value">
                        <%= client %>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <%= typeof department !=='undefined' ? department : '' %>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <%= typeof email !=='undefined' ? email : '' %>
                    </div>
                </td>
                <td class="vertical-text">CONSIGNEE</td>
                <td colspan="3">
                    <div class="value">
                        <%= receiver_name %>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <%= receiver_address %>
                    </div>
                    <span class="label" style="display:inline">Pincode:</span> <span class="value">
                        <%= delivery_pin_code %>
                    </span>
                    <span class="label" style="display:inline; margin-left:10px;">Mob:</span> <span class="value">
                        <%= mobile_number %>
                    </span>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>

        <table>
            <tr>
                <td colspan="3" class="bg-grey"><span class="label">WEIGHT</span></td>
                <td>
                    <%= weight %>
                        <%= type==='DOX' ? 'Gms' : 'Kg' %>
                </td>
                <td colspan="4" rowspan="7" style="font-size: 7.5px;">
                    <div style="color:red; font-weight:bold; text-decoration:underline;">CONDITIONS OF CARRIAGE:</div>
                    1. <b>Said to Contain Basis:</b> All consignments are booked on "said to contain basis". Company is
                    not liable for description/contents.<br>
                    2. <b>Prohibited Items:</b> Currency, jewelry, explosives, and contraband are strictly
                    prohibited.<br>
                    3. <b>Liability:</b> Max liability for loss/damage is limited to ₹100 for documents or 5x freight
                    for parcels.<br>
                    4. <b>No Service Area:</b> If booked for NSA, shipment will be returned at consignor's cost.
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td colspan="3" class="bg-grey"><span class="label">VOLUMETRIC WEIGHT</span></td>
                <td>
                    <%= typeof vol_weight !=='undefined' ? vol_weight : '0.00' %>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td colspan="3" class="bg-grey"><span class="label">FREIGHT CHARGE</span></td>
                <td>₹<%= price %>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td colspan="3" class="bg-grey"><span class="label">PACKAGE CHARGE</span></td>
                <td>₹<%= package_charge %>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td colspan="3" class="bg-grey"><span class="label">INSURANCE CHARGE</span></td>
                <td>₹<%= typeof insurance_value !=='undefined' ? insurance_value : '0' %>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td colspan="3" class="bg-grey"><span class="label">E-WAY BILL NO</span></td>
                <td>
                    <%= typeof eway_bill !=='undefined' ? eway_bill : 'N/A' %>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="total-row">
                <td colspan="3">TOTAL CHARGE</td>
                <td>₹<%= total_amount %>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>

        <table>
            <tr style="height: 40px;">
                <td colspan="4"><span class="label">CONSIGNOR SIGNATURE</span></td>
                <td colspan="4"><span class="label">RECEIVED BY (Name & Stamp)</span></td>
            </tr>
        </table>

        <div class="conditions-box">
            <div class="conditions-title">FULL TERMS AND CONDITIONS OF CARRIAGE</div>
            5. Applicability: The provision set out and referred to in this consignment note shall apply to
            transportation through any mode.
            6. Definitions: (a) SMILE - SHREE MARUTI INTEGRATED LOGISTICS LIMITED (b) Customer - means and includes
            consignor, consignee and/or his/her authorized representatives.
            7. Contract: The docket is a contract between the company and the customer.
            8. Non-Negotiable: The Consignment Note is non-negotiable and the consignor acknowledges that it has been
            prepared by the Consignor or by Company on behalf of the Consignor.
            9. Acceptance of Terms: By giving us your shipment you accept our terms and conditions.
            10. Insurance: SMILE does not offer any insurance cover for shipments; customer must hand over insured goods
            for transportation under consignor insurance.
            11. Law & Jurisdiction: This contract shall be governed by Indian Law and all disputes subject to Jaipur
            jurisdiction.
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/jsbarcode@3.11.5/dist/JsBarcode.all.min.js"></script>
    <script>
        JsBarcode("#barcode", "<%= document_number %>", {
            format: "CODE128",
            width: 1.2,
            height: 30,
            displayValue: false,
            margin: 0
        });
    </script>

</body>

</html>